    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰考虑如何使用苹果未支付的 130 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/ireland-to-decide-how-to-use-13-billion-it-said-it-didn-t-want</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰刚刚面临一项令大多数国家羡慕的挑战：如何花掉苹果公司被欧盟最高法院勒令缴纳的近 138 亿欧元（152 亿美元）的意外之财。这笔钱相当于今年政府支出的 14%，相当于每个男人、女人和孩子约 2,700 欧元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/ireland-to-decide-how-to-use-13-billion-it-said-it-didn-t-want</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 15:07:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国福利削减引发愤怒 斯塔默之战迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/starmer-fends-off-labour-rebellion-over-uk-pensioner-benefit-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 决定取消大多数英国养老金领取者的冬季燃料补贴，导致其政府遭到强烈反对，他所在的工党也向他发出了警告，称他在试图修复英国公共财政时将面临艰难的战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/starmer-fends-off-labour-rebellion-over-uk-pensioner-benefit-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 14:36:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
